description: Excellent T3 with balcony, ready to debut, inserted in the iconic Emporium building, in Porto, consisting of: - Entrance hall, common room with 34.2 m2 with access to a balcony, kitchen, laundry, a suite overlooking the interior garden and 2 suites with access to a balcony facing Rua Guedes Azevedo. - Fix - 2 parking spaces Apartment inserted in the emblematic Emporium Building, on the corner of Ruas Sá da Bandeira and Guedes de Azevedo, where an exclusive luxury condominium was born with only 23 apartments from T1 to T4 typologies, with parking and a large private garden with more than 800 m2. With finishes that excel in detail and superior quality, the project is based on full comfort, with each room in the Emporium Building having solid brown wood floors, marble bathrooms, solid wood window frames with double glazing and sophisticated Boffi kitchens fully equipped with Gaggenau and Siemens appliances. The Emporium is one of the most charismatic buildings on Rua Sá da Bandeira, designed by the architect José Porto and built in 1948 to be a building of great prestige, which was achieved through the solidity of reinforced concrete and the careful selection of noble materials, combined with the modern appearance of the layout and the dignity of classical architecture. The intervention of the architect Duarte Morais Soares, preserved the history of the Emporium but, by including an exclusive garden with more than 800 m2 inside, with large-scale trees and a private garage, it allows residents to live peacefully in the center of the city. The Emporium translates the best of downtown. The surroundings have a traditional neighborhood atmosphere, but are just minutes away from all the reasons why you choose to live in Porto. Located in a very central area, close to Mercado do Bolhão and Rua de Santa Catarina, the city's main commercial artery, the Emporium also has other advantages such as proximity to teaching facilities and a public transport network, with two stations Metro nearby, as well as a diversified cultural and leisure offer, placing you at the center of all the activity in Baixa. Unique project in a privileged location that presents itself as a safe investment and an attractive opportunity for those who want to.
